title: Ancient Egypt 2019 12 x 12 Inch Monthly Square Wall Calendar, Travel Egypt Pyramids Cairo Giza
features: The glorious civilization of ancient Egypt sprang up along the banks of the north Nile around 3500 B.C.E. and flourished for over 3,000 years. The ancient Egyptians inspired timeless legends and built marvelous structures that still stand as testaments to their inventive spirit. Featuring pyramids, the Sphinx, and other timeless attractions, this captivating square wall calendar surveys some of ancient Egypt’s most stunning sights.
– Enjoy beautiful, award-winning photographs every single month •
– Printed with sustainable, soy-based inks on Forest Stewardship Council-certified paper •
– Prevents curled corners due to moisture, avoids ink bleed-through, and stays secure on your wall, and durable binding lasts throughout the year •
– All major holidays listed, with plenty of room for writing notes and appointments •
Great as a Gift or to Keep Yourself Organized
